cast.overview: The UK Prime Minister and US President have a public rivalry that risks their countries' alliance. But when they become targets of a powerful enemy, they're forced to rely on each other as they go on a wild, multinational run. Allied with Noel, a brilliant MI6 agent, they must find a way to thwart a conspiracy that threatens the free world.
cast.title: Heads of State

cast.overview: After his career is destroyed, a brilliant but arrogant surgeon gets a new lease on life when a sorcerer takes him under her wing and trains him to defend the world against evil.
cast.title: Doctor Strange

details.biography: Katrina Durden is a British actress, martial artist and stuntwoman.  Her first noteworthy role was as the main antagonist in the Street Fighter: Resurrection TV series with Machinima. She was most recently cast as the role of The Blonde Zealot in Marvel’s Doctor Strange.
details.name: Katrina Durden
